text.tspan: In summary, combining modern techniques from analytical
chemistry, food science, biochemistry, synthetic biology, color
science, and computational chemistry, we found,
characterized, and defined a path to production for a
naturally sourced cyan blue colorant whose color properties are
nearly identical to those of the industry standard brilliant blue
